data.title: Mozilla Monitor
data.meta_description: Find out if you’ve been part of a data breach with ⁨Mozilla Monitor⁩. We’ll help you understand what to do next and continuously monitor for any new breaches.
data.text:
We’ll help you fix your exposures

Our mission is to put control of your personal data back in your hands. We’ll help you resolve data breaches and keep your info private — and we’ll respect your privacy in the process.

Enter your email address to check for data breach exposures.

What info could be at risk?

Data leaks are unfortunately part of our digital lives. Your passwords, contact details, financial information, and other personal info can be exposed, putting you at risk of identity theft.

Enter your email address to check for data breach exposures.
